title: Dovecot mail server status
agents: linux
catalog: app/dovecot
license: GPL
distribution: arsoft
description:
 The check determinate the current state of the Dovecot mail server.

item:
  The item {daemon} shows the daemon status.

  The item {statistics} collect statistics information of the mail server.

inventory:
  Returns two checks for each machine: {daemon} and {statistics}
